AUTHOR     (G.M.Raisbeck,J.Lestringuez,F.Yiou)
TITLE      Cross sections for Li-6 and Li-7 production from the
           bombardment of C-12 by 150- and 600-MeV protons and
           880-MeV alpha particles
FACILITY   (SYNCY,2FR PAR) 150 MeV Protons
           (SYNCY,2ZZZCER) 600 MeV Protons
           (SYNCY,1USABRK) 880 MeV alphas
SAMPLE     High-purity carbon plaques
METHOD     (ACTIV,INTB)
DETECTOR   (MAGSP)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) The uncertainty in estimating slopes of
           measured Li-7/Li-6 ratio as a function of time elapsed
           between irradiation and analysis, together with
           uncertainty in Be-7 cross sections, were combined to
           give errors for Li-6 and Li-7 cross sections.
STATUS     (TABLE,,G.M.Raisbeck+,J,PR/C,6,685,1972)
            Data taken from PR/C,6,685,1972--table I.
HISTORY    (19870423C)
           (20260121A) OS. FACILITY updated, other BIB updates,
            converted to lower and upper case
